# Agent Assist Brand Guidelines

**Governance:** Internal Use Only. This rule is the authoritative brand reference. All new components must align; deviations require design approval.

**Personality:** Modern, technical, trustworthy, enterprise-grade, AI-forward but human-readable. Clean layouts, strong hierarchy, neutral foundations with confident accents. Clarity over decoration.

---

## Design Tokens

### Light mode — Colors
| Role | Value | Use |
|------|--------|-----|
| Brand Primary | `#2563EB` | Primary buttons, links, active |
| Dark Ink | `#0F172A` | Headings, key content |
| Neutral 900 | `#111827` | Headings |
| Neutral 700 | `#374151` | Body text |
| Neutral 500 | `#6B7280` | Descriptions, placeholders |
| Neutral 200 | `#E5E7EB` | Borders, dividers |
| Neutral 100 | `#F3F4F6` | Card backgrounds |
| Accent Teal | `#14B8A6` | Icons, hover, focus |
| Success | `#22C55E` | Success states |
| Warning | `#F59E0B` | Warnings |
| Error | `#EF4444` | Errors |
| Info | `#3B82F6` | Notices |

### Dark mode — Surfaces & text
- **Surfaces:** Base `#020617`, Raised (cards) `#0F172A`, Elevated (hover) slightly lighter, Overlay translucent black.
- **Brand:** Primary `#3B82F6`, Accent `#2DD4BF`, Muted `#60A5FA`.
- **Text:** Primary `#E5E7EB`, Secondary `#CBD5E1`, Tertiary `#94A3B8`, Disabled `#64748B`.
- **Rule:** Never use full-brightness semantic colors on dark backgrounds; use muted/safe variants.

### Typography
- **Font:** Inter, fallback system sans-serif.
- **Scale:** XL 48px Bold (hero), L 36px Bold (sections), M 28px SemiBold (features), S 22px SemiBold (cards), Body L 18px, Body M 16px (default), Body S 14px, Caption 12px.

### Spacing (px)
- XS 4, SM 8, MD 16, LG 32, XL 64, XXL 96. Use for icon padding (XS), tight UI (SM), default (MD), section gaps (LG–XXL).

