## Components

**Buttons**
- Primary: filled, Brand Primary bg. Secondary: outline. Tertiary: text only.
- Heights: S 36px, M 44px (default), L 52px (hero). Dark: primary = brand bg + white text; secondary = transparent + brand outline; tertiary = muted text, brightens on hover. Disabled: low contrast, no glow.

**Cards**
- Radius `8px`, padding `24px`, light neutral border, subtle shadow. Dark: Surface/Raised bg, Neutral 700 border, very subtle shadow; hover = Surface/Elevated.

**Icons**
- Line/outline style, consistent stroke; sizes 16 / 24 / 32px. Dark: Neutral 500 or Brand Accent; illustrations lower contrast.

---

## Accessibility (non-negotiable)
- Minimum touch target **44px**.
- Text contrast **WCAG AA**.
- Focus states **always visible**. Dark: avoid pure black; no light grey text on dark grey; focus rings clearly visible.

When styling dashboards, widgets, or new UI, use these tokens in Tailwind (or CSS variables) and follow the component and accessibility rules above.
